## 🎨 Proposed Mobile-First Redesign

### Header Structure
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│ [←] TapScore Logo          [≡]      │ ← Fairway Green (#1B4332)
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                     │
│   📸 Hero Banner (if available)     │ ← Optional banner with overlay
│   📍 Östgöta H40 2025              │ ← White text on image
│                                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 📅 Season Info | 🏆 Teams | 📊 Stats│ ← Light Rough (#95D5B2) info bar
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Navigation Strategy
**Replace horizontal scrolling tabs with:**
1. **Primary Content Area**: Overview/Landing document (default)
2. **Bottom Sheet Navigation**: Slide-up panels for secondary content
3. **Quick Action Buttons**: Strategic placement for key actions

### Content Layout Priority
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│ 1. HERO SECTION                     │
│   - Series name + banner            │
│   - Key stats in info bar           │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 2. PRIMARY CONTENT                  │
│   - Landing document OR             │
│   - Welcome message + quick cards   │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 3. QUICK ACCESS CARDS               │
│   [📋 Latest Results] [📅 Next Event]│
│   [🏆 Standings] [📄 Documents]     │
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ 4. RECENT ACTIVITY                  │
│   - Latest competition results      │
│   - Recent standings changes        │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Navigation Patterns
- **Primary Tab**: Overview (always visible)
- **Secondary Access**: Bottom sheet or dedicated pages
- **Deep Links**: Direct access to standings, competitions, documents

