## 📱 Detailed Component Specifications

### 1. Header Component
```css
.series-header {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--fairway-green), var(--turf-green));
  color: var(--scorecard-white);
  padding: 1rem;
}

.hero-banner {
  height: 200px;
  border-radius: 1rem;
  background-size: cover;
  position: relative;
}

.hero-overlay {
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.7));
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  border-radius: 1rem;
}

.series-title {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
```

### 2. Info Bar Component
```css
.info-bar {
  background: var(--light-rough);
  border-radius: 1rem;
  padding: 1rem;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}

.info-item {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--charcoal-text);
}

.info-value {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
